Standard Deployment:
  Step 1: Build full stack images
    docker compose -f docker-compose.full.yml build

  Step 2: Deploy with node-agent scaling
    docker compose -f docker-compose.full.yml up -d --scale node-agent=5

  Step 3: Verify all services
    docker compose -f docker-compose.full.yml ps

  Step 4: Check resource usage
    docker stats

Scaling:
  Scale to 5 node agents:
    docker compose -f docker-compose.full.yml up -d --scale node-agent=5

  Scale to 10 node agents:
    docker compose -f docker-compose.full.yml up -d --scale node-agent=10

  Monitor scaling:
    watch -n 5 'docker compose -f docker-compose.full.yml ps'

Backup & Recovery:
  Backup backend data volume:
    docker run --rm -v sovereign_map_federated_learning_backend_data:/data -v $(pwd):/backup busybox tar czf /backup/backend_data.tar.gz -C /data .

  Restore backend data volume:
    docker run --rm -v sovereign_map_federated_learning_backend_data:/data -v $(pwd):/backup busybox tar xzf /backup/backend_data.tar.gz -C /data
